            "title": "A股半日跌1%  有色金屬股跌停",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日跌約1%，深股曾跌破14000，兩市成交合計19329.05億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-17.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-17.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指半日跌49點或1.19%，報4108點，今早開報4131 點，跌0.63%，早段見4152點，跌5點或0.12%，為半日高位，約10:30AM見4064點，跌93點或2.24%，為半日低位，半日成交8636.52億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指半日報14162點，跌137點或0.96%，開報14214 點，跌0.60%，最高見14272點，跌28點或0.02，其後跌勢加劇，中段見13923，挫377點或2.64%，為半日低位，半日成交10692.53億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日逆升26點或0.8%，滬深300半日跌48點或1.01%，報4705點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">有色金屬股大跌，近30股跌停。</p>\n</div>",
